statements: SELECT user_id, eye_image, scan_date, detected_disease FROM retina_scanning_data WHERE user_id = 1;
SELECT scan_date, detected_disease, eye_image, user_id FROM retina_scanning_data WHERE detected_disease = 'Glaucoma';
SELECT user_id, scan_date FROM retina_scanning_data WHERE user_id > 5 ORDER BY scan_date DESC;
SELECT user_id, detected_disease FROM retina_scanning_data WHERE detected_disease IS NOT NULL ORDER BY user_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM retina_scanning_data WHERE scan_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM retina_scanning_data WHERE user_id = 1;
SELECT user_id, scan_date, detected_disease FROM retina_scanning_data WHERE scan_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT user_id, detected_disease FROM retina_scanning_data WHERE detected_disease LIKE 'Diabetes%';
SELECT * FROM retina_scanning_data ORDER BY scan_date DESC;
SELECT COUNT(user_id), detected_disease FROM retina_scanning_data GROUP BY detected_disease;
SELECT * FROM RetinaScanningData;
SELECT patient_id, patient_name FROM RetinaScanningData WHERE scan_date = '2022-01-15';
SELECT disease_name, description FROM EyeDiseases WHERE disease_id = 1;
SELECT patient_name, scan_date FROM RetinaScanningData ORDER BY scan_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM RetinaScanningData WHERE patient_id = 100 AND scan_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT patient_name, scan_date FROM RetinaScanningData WHERE patient_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM RetinaScanningData ORDER BY scan_date DESC;
SELECT patient_name, disease_name, description FROM RetinaScanningData JOIN EyeDiseases ON RetinaScanningData.patient_id = EyeDiseases.disease_id;
SELECT * FROM RetinaScanningData WHERE scan_date >= '2022-01-01' AND scan_date <= '2022-12-31';
SELECT MAX(scan_date) AS latest_scan_date FROM RetinaScanningData;
SELECT user_id, username, email, age FROM RetinaUsers;
SELECT image_id, user_id, image_url, timestamp FROM RetinaImages ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT analysis_id, image_id, diagnosis, confidence FROM RetinaAnalysis WHERE confidence > 0.8;
SELECT username, email FROM RetinaUsers WHERE age > 30;
SELECT * FROM RetinaImages JOIN RetinaUsers ON RetinaImages.user_id = RetinaUsers.user_id;
SELECT * FROM RetinaUsers;
SELECT user_id, username FROM RetinaUsers WHERE age > 30;
SELECT * FROM RetinaImages ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT image_url, diagnosis FROM RetinaAnalysis JOIN RetinaImages ON RetinaAnalysis.image_id = RetinaImages.image_id;

SELECT user_id, username, email, age, image_url, diagnosis, confidence FROM RetinaUsers JOIN RetinaImages ON RetinaUsers.user_id = RetinaImages.user_id JOIN RetinaAnalysis ON RetinaImages.image_id = RetinaAnalysis.image_id WHERE confidence > 0.8;
SELECT * FROM RetinaScanningData;
SELECT patient_id, scan_date, scan_result FROM RetinaScanningData ORDER BY scan_date DESC;
SELECT disease_name, description FROM EyeDiseases WHERE disease_id = 1;
SELECT clinic_name, location FROM Clinic WHERE location = 'New York';
SELECT patient_id, disorder_name, diagnosis_date FROM EyeDisorders WHERE disorder_id > 5 ORDER BY diagnosis_date ASC;
SELECT * FROM RetinaScanningData;
SELECT patient_id, scan_result, scan_date FROM RetinaScanningData ORDER BY scan_date DESC;
SELECT e.disease_name, d.description FROM EyeDiseases e JOIN EyeDisorders ed ON e.disease_id = ed.disorder_id;
SELECT r.patient_id, r.scan_date, c.clinic_name FROM RetinaScanningData r JOIN Clinic c ON r.scan_date < '2021-01-01';
SELECT r.patient_id, COUNT(ed.disorder_id) AS num_disorders FROM RetinaScanningData r LEFT JOIN EyeDisorders ed ON r.patient_id = ed.patient_id GROUP BY r.patient_id HAVING num_disorders > 1;
SELECT * FROM RetinaImages;
SELECT image_id, patient_id, scan_date FROM RetinaImages ORDER BY scan_date DESC;
SELECT first_name, last_name FROM Patients WHERE age > 50;
SELECT condition_id, patient_id, diagnosis_date FROM EyeConditions WHERE patient_id = 123;
SELECT analysis_id, analysis_date FROM ImageAnalysis WHERE analysis_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-03-31';
SELECT * FROM RetinaImages WHERE scan_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT patient_id, MAX(age) FROM Patients GROUP BY patient_id;
SELECT i.image_id, p.first_name, p.last_name, p.age, i.scan_date FROM RetinaImages i JOIN Patients p ON i.patient_id = p.patient_id;
SELECT condition_name, COUNT(*) FROM EyeConditions GROUP BY condition_name HAVING COUNT(*) > 1;
SELECT c.clinician_id, c.first_name, c.last_name, COUNT(a.analysis_id) AS analysis_count FROM Clinicians c LEFT JOIN ImageAnalysis a ON c.clinician_id = a.analysis_id GROUP BY c.clinician_id;
